(3, 12, '"Read the conversation and answer the questions.\r\nAt school\r\nMary : Do you have any pets?\r\nKate : Yes, I have a small dog.\r\nMary : What kind of dog is it?\r\nKate : It is a puddle. Do you have any pets at home?\r\nMary : Yes, I have two cats. They can catch rats very well. What can your dog do?\r\nKate : It can sit, shake hands and roll over.\r\n\r\nWhich sentence is true?"\r\n', 'Kate has two cats.', 'Mary has a small dog.', 'Mary’s pets can catch rats very well.', 'Kate’s pet can sit and catch rats very well.', 'Mary’s pets can catch rats very well.\r\n', 'สัตว์เลี้ยงของ Mary เป็น แมวจึงจับแมวได้เก่ง'),
(3, 13, '"Your friend asks you what you think about his new telephone.\r\nYou say : __________"\r\n', 'Is it yours?', 'I also have one.', 'It’s nice.', 'Can I use it?', 'It’s nice.\r\n', 'It s nice เป็นคำตอบที่เหมาะสมกว่า I also have one'),
(3, 14, '"Joe : There’s a new Japanese restaurant on the corner.\r\nMike : Really? Have you tried it?\r\nJoe : Of course, I went there yesterday.\r\nMike : How was it?\r\nJoe : __________."\r\n', 'It isn’t far from here', 'My friend is a waiter there', 'You can walk there', 'The food is good and cheap', 'The food is good and cheap\r\n', 'คำถามของ Mike ถามว่าร้านเป็นยังไง จึงต้องตอบ The food is good and cheap '),
(3, 15, '"Harry and Julia are in the classroom.\r\nHarry : Our new English teacher comes to teach us today.\r\nJulia : __________.\r\nHarry : She’s quite tall and beautiful."\r\n', 'What does she like?', 'What does she look like?', 'What is she looking at?', 'What is she looking for?', 'What does she look like?\r\n', 'คำตอบของ Harry ตอบเป็นลักษณะรูปร่าง คำถามจึงต้องตอบเป็น look like?'),
(3, 16, '"Bee : You look __________ today. Why?\r\nAmy : I am the winner of English Speech Contest."\r\n', 'angry', 'tried', 'happy', 'sad', 'happy\r\n', 'Amy ชนะ จึงต้องรู้สึก Happy'),
(3, 17, '"There / kinds / are / teachers / school / our / in / many\r\nWhich sentence is correct?"\r\n', 'There are many teachers kinds in our school.', 'There are many kinds teachers in our school', 'There are kinds many teachers in our school.\r\n', 'There are teachers many kinds in our school.', 'There are many kinds teachers in our school.', 'คำตอบถูกต้องตาม Grammar'),
